dieval (swords and magic) mixed with futuristic (space ships and stuff...) era. I think the story needs much work..<br>
<br>
K...There is this universe named Luminaire. It consists of several planets. One of the biggest  planets uses a special mineral to use as currency. The mineral grows on a smaller, weaker planet and only there. Every once in a while the bigger planet runs out of 'currency' and borrows some from the smaller one. But now the growing of minerals is late and the small planet is getting weaker, for the mineral keeps the planet living. So the 'leader' of the weak planet refuses to give the leader for the bigger planet minerals. This gets the strong planet leader angry and he declares war on the small planet. <br>
 <br>
<br>
Before all this, the small planets' leader was different, and he was totally prejudiced against anyone from the big planet. A small band of exiles from the bigger planet come to this smaller planet, with nowhere else to go.  The leader of the smaller planets orders them to leave or be killed. So a resident of the small planets' biggest city, Shraik Moode (Strange name... I'm kinda attached..) takes them in and hides them. The travellers decide to live with Shraik in his small hut. Three years later, an officer of the planet asks Shraik about a boy that happens to live in his house. But before he could answer the officer pulled out his weapon and fired all around the area for no apparent reason. <br>
<br>
So they escape and go into the big city. There they split up and Shraik and one of the members of the group get caught by another officer. As the officer holds them up a dark figure moves through the crowd and, stealthily kills the officer. So through the story Shraik and the exiles try and find out what is wrong with the officers, who the dark figure is. Meanwhile the current leader looks for soldiers throughout the small planet. He comes upon several warriors. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=psychosoldier>Psycho Soldier</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(1/31/02 5:02:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=477.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new story idea....Bland and unoriginal?</span><hr size=1> The rough idea is fine.<br>
